title: BBC Adventure Show: Scotland - Coast to Coast PDTV x264-MVGroup
description:
BBC The Adventure Show 2011 Scotland: Coast to Coast PDTV x264-MVGroup

Starting on Aberdeen's beach and finishing in the wild lands of Knoydart in the west, Cameron McNeish travels through Scotland's most spectacular glens and mountains following a new route that proves that Scotland has some of the most outstanding landscapes in the world.

This 200 mile walk includes an ascent of both the most easterly and most westerly mainland Munros, a diversion down memory lane, a crossing of two of Scotland's highest mountain passes and a treasure hunt for some wild cats.
